An object-oriented model of an RDF graph.

Package gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2 Description

An object-oriented model of an RDF graph.

See Model for the root of the API, and also Models for Model factories.

RDF typing rules are supported. See "Discussion on the semantics of rdfs:Resource, rdfs:Class, rdf:Property" for a reference of these rules.
